# device-backups holds device-state captures. DEFAULT-DENY: ignore everything,
# then allow only files reviewed and confirmed free of secrets/PII. The
# BoseApp-Persistence tarball contains a private key, WiFi credentials, an auth
# token, and personal identity — it must never be committed.
device-backups/*
!device-backups/SoundTouchSdkPrivateCfg.xml.orig
!device-backups/presets-original.xml

# Build output
preset-server-armv7

# Local operational notes: real device identifiers + passwordless-root SSH
# access details. Must never be published. Kept local-only.
SESSION-HANDOFF.md
